# Horizontal Rules Examples in Zolt

## Basic Separators

Three types of horizontal rules:

---
Standard separator (three dashes)

***
Thick separator (three asterisks)

___
Thin separator (three underscores)

## Styled Separators

Separators with attributes:

--- {color=red}
Red separator

*** {color=blue}
Blue thick separator

___ {color=green}
Green thin separator

## Dashed Separators

Different styles:

--- {style=dashed}
Dashed separator

--- {style=dotted}
Dotted separator

--- {style=solid}
Solid separator (default)

## Width Variations

Different widths:

--- {width=50%}
50% width separator

--- {width=200px}
200 pixel width separator

--- {width=30em}
30 em width separator

## Alignment

Separator alignment:

--- {align=left}
Left aligned

--- {align=center}
Center aligned

--- {align=right}
Right aligned

## Combined Styling

Multiple attributes together:

--- {color=blue style=dashed width=80%}
Blue dashed 80% width

*** {color=red style=solid width=300px align=center}
Red solid 300px centered

___ {color=purple style=dotted width=60% align=right}
Purple dotted 60% right

